<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>close down • shut down</xh5><p> <i>close down—</i>1. <i>(of a shop, factory, etc.)</i> cease doing business; stop production: The shop will be <u>closing down</u> for good on Saturday, so everything is half price. 2. <i>(of a radio or TV station)</i> stop broadcasting for the day: This station is now <u>closing down</u> and we wish you all good-night.</p><p> <i>shut down</i>— = close down 1: The whole company <u>shuts down</u> for three weeks’ holiday every year.</p> </entry>
